text: Flavour is spot on but portion is a little smaller than expected. We felt that we had bigger portion when we dined in, psychological? The Trilogia dips (Tirokafteri, Santorinia, and Tarama) are awesome especially Tarama, the one cod roe.

Unfortunately food was cold, order was not planned well as many items were sitting on the side getting cold whilst waiting for 1 more to be finished.

Price to Portion size was way off, making it rather pricey. e.g. $19 for 4 thin pieces of Dolmades is frankly a bit NUTS!

However, after reheating the takeaway at home, the lamb kebab and pork souvlaki were tasty.
They since like only available for delivery.
